things vaguely related to the filesystem

 * findin - applies glob expressions to PATH (or MANPATH or whatever)
 * findup - searches up directories for something
 * getpof - searches down a directory tree (possibly for .git)
 * is-changed - you probably instead want entr(1)
 * rename - yet another version of this Larry Wall script
 * repod - makes git repositories go various places eg to a remote host
   or bare repo elsewhere
